adbWireless enable ADB wireless connection to connect to the phone as if connected by USB.

used a method already known to enable the wireless connection through:

03-17-2010: http://goo.gl/iK77
04-10-2010: http://goo.gl/Z03r
04-12-2010: http://goo.gl/GoyF

Change log v1.2.1 by Filip

Portrait only 
Added haptic feedback and made it optional
Turn USB-debugging back on in adbstop()
Save mState to get true indication if running or not when the app starts.

Rooted Phone Only!!!

